title: Man-Cave | Watch: Here's the crowd at UFC Dublin singing with Aisling Daly during her walkout
text:
Although last night's UFC Fight Night 76 ended in disappointment for Paddy Holohan and Cathal Pendred, Aisling Daly had a convincing victory over Brazil's Ericka Almeida.
Daly destroyed Almeida convincingly with a unanimous decision win. Almeida's record is now seven wins and two losses, with Daly going 2-1 in the UFC.
Her walkout song, Cranberries' Zombie, played through the 3Arena and, sure enough, the capacity crowd rowed in behind her.
Take a look.
You can see Aisling's chat with Mike on The Manual right here where she discusses preparation for her fight and her training regime.
Wish that commentator would have just kept schtum and let the moment breathe, though.
Via Streamable
